Upper-intermediate+ English, both written and spoken is a must
Very good communication and presentation skills;
Strong knowledge of MS Office suite (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Visio) backed by usage experience;
Some experience in project coordination
Quick and self-motivated learner;
