● Have a structured, analytical thinking and come up with new innovative ideas;
● Are familiar with complex technical architectures and understand cards related technologies;
● Have good presentation skills;
● Are focused on finding solutions and on achieving results;
● Can easily and clearly communicate with vendors, business lines and IT colleagues;
● Can create good work relations based on trust and responsibility;
● Act as a team player, energetic with a desire to learn and progress

